    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּיוֹם טוֹב. <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Abba bar Abba here. He, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"17\" data-full-name=\"Abba bar Abba here. He\" data-name-he=\"אבא בר אבא אבוה דשמואל\">אֲבוּהּ דִּשְׁמוּאֵל</span> אָמַר: אֲפִילּוּ גִּלְגֵּל",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עִיסָּה מֵעֶ<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רֶב</span> יוֹם טוֹב — אֵין מַפְרִישׁ מִמֶּנָּה",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "חַלָּתָהּ בְּיוֹם טוֹב. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>לֵימָא פְּלִיגָא <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">דִּשְׁמוּאֵל</span> אַדַּאֲבוּהּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "(דִּשְׁמוּאֵל). דְּאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">שְׁמוּאֵל</span>: חַלַּת חוּצָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לָאָרֶץ, אוֹכֵל וְהוֹלֵךְ וְאַחַר כָּךְ מַפְרִישׁ! <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rava, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rava\" data-name-he=\"רָבָא\">רָבָא</span>:",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִי לֹא מוֹדֶה <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">שְׁמוּאֵל</span> שֶׁאִם קָרָא עָלֶיהָ שֵׁם",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁאֲסוּרָה לְזָרִים? <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"9\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"20\" data-sentence-id=\"3\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"א\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Shammai, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2756\" data-full-name=\"Beit Shammai\" data-name-he=\"בית שמאי\">בֵּית שַׁמַּאי</span> אוֹמְרִים:",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֵין מוֹלִיכִין אֶת הַסּוּלָּם מִשּׁוֹבָךְ לְשׁוֹבָךְ,",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲבָל מַטֵּהוּ מֵחַלּוֹן לְחַלּוֹן. <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Hillel, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"963\" data-full-name=\"Beit Hillel\" data-name-he=\"בית הלל\">וּבֵית הִלֵּל</span> מַתִּירִין.",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"10\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"21\" data-sentence-id=\"4\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ב\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Ḥanin bar Ashi I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1314\" data-full-name=\"Rav Ḥanin bar Ashi I\" data-name-he=\"רב חנן בר אמי\">רַב חָנָן בַּר אַמֵּי</span>: מַחְלוֹקֶת",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בִּרְשׁוּת הָ<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רַבּ</span>ִים, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Shammai, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2756\" data-full-name=\"Beit Shammai\" data-name-he=\"בית שמאי\">דְּבֵית שַׁמַּאי</span> סָבְרִי: הָרוֹאֶה אוֹמֵר",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְהָטִיחַ גַּגּוֹ הוּא צָרִיךְ, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Hillel, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"963\" data-full-name=\"Beit Hillel\" data-name-he=\"בית הלל\">וּבֵית הִלֵּל</span> סָבְרִי: שׁוֹבָכוֹ",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מוֹכִיחַ עָלָיו. אֲבָל בִּרְשׁוּת הַיָּחִיד — דִּבְרֵי הַכֹּל",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מוּתָּר. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אִינִי? וְהָא אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1394\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel\" data-name-he=\"רב יהודה בר יחזקאל\">רַב יְהוּדָה</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רַב</span>:",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כׇּל מָקוֹם שֶׁאָסְרוּ חֲכָמִים מִפְּנֵי מַרְאִית",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הָעַיִן, אֲפִילּוּ בְּחַדְרֵי חֲדָרִים אָסוּר! תַּנָּאֵי הִיא.",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּתַנְיָא: שׁוֹטְחָן בַּחַמָּה, אֲבָל לֹא כְּנֶגֶד הָעָם.",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi, sixth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1508\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה הנשיא\">רַבִּי</span> (אֱלִיעֶזֶר) <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">וְרַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span> אוֹסְרִין. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אִיכָּא דְּאָמְרִי,",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Ḥanin bar Ashi I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1314\" data-full-name=\"Rav Ḥanin bar Ashi I\" data-name-he=\"רב חנן בר אמי\">רַב חָנָן בַּר אַמֵּי</span>: מַחְלוֹקֶת בִּרְשׁוּת הַיָּחִיד, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Shammai, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2756\" data-full-name=\"Beit Shammai\" data-name-he=\"בית שמאי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-15756\">דְּבֵית</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
