      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Shammai, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2756\" data-full-name=\"Beit Shammai\" data-name-he=\"בית שמאי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-15756\">שַׁמַּאי</span> אִית לְהוּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1394\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel\" data-name-he=\"רב יהודה בר יחזקאל\">דְּרַב יְהוּדָה</span> אָמַר רַב, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Hillel, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"963\" data-full-name=\"Beit Hillel\" data-name-he=\"בית הלל\">וּבֵית הִלֵּל</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לֵית לְהוּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1394\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel\" data-name-he=\"רב יהודה בר יחזקאל\">דְּרַב יְהוּדָה</span> אָמַר רַב, אֲבָל בִּרְשׁוּת הָרַבִּים —",
