      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Shammai, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2756\" data-full-name=\"Beit Shammai\" data-name-he=\"בית שמאי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-15763\">שַׁמַּאי</span>? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תַּנָּאֵי הִיא, דְּתַנְיָא: שׁוֹטְחָן בַּחַמָּה, אֲבָל",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לֹא כְּנֶגֶד הָעָם. <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi, sixth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1508\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה הנשיא\">רַבִּי</span> (אֱלִיעֶזֶר) <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">וְרַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span> אוֹסְרִין.",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    }
  ],
